### Step-by-Step Integration Plan

1. **Fork the repo** into your own GitHub
1. **Clone it locally** — open `index.html` in browser to confirm it works with Wikipedia first
1. **Create `js/fractal_api.js`** — replaces `wikipedia_parse.js`, points to your backend
1. **Update `index.html`** — swap `wikipedia_parse.js` script tag for `fractal_api.js`
1. **Restyle** — update CSS files and welcome text for Fractal branding
1. **Update node colors** in `main_functions.js` to match Fractal’s color scheme
1. **Test locally** with Ollama backend running
1. **Deploy** pointing to Groq backend for the live demo

